casebody.data:
Kenneth P. Kellogg v. Molly E. Kellogg Stephen A. Wise, for the appellee (defendant). Robert G. Bell, Jr., for the appellant (plaintiff). Robert G. Bell, Jr., in support of the motion. Argued January 3 decided January 3, 1978 Submitted January 3

decided January 3, 1978

The defendant’s motion, filed November 21, 1977, to dismiss the appeal from the Superior Court in Fairfield County at Stamford is granted by the court.

The plaintiff’s motion for an order to the Superior Court in Fairfield County at Stamford “to make findings” is dismissed by the court.
